y personal shelter. This is where I feel safe to present myself to people - where I feel comfortable enough to communicate my opinions, to build relationships, and to send peace and love. And I hope everyone who walks in will feel the same way. <br> </p></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-a94d" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-hAcGzb jHOovW pf-730_"><div style="--cw:801px" class="sc-eGPXGI cIlovf"><div class="sc-iCfMLu eehqFj pf-731_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;--s-lg:0px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-XxNYO eWQzGj pf-732_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0654/0725/4745/files/1_c44dacd2-eb38-4931-be67-5f88c89be368_386x.png?v=1707202910" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0654/0725/4745/files/1_c44dacd2-eb38-4931-be67-5f88c89be368.png?v=1707202910 1536w" width="735" height="1124" sizes="(min-width: 1536px) 1536px, (min-width: 1024px) 1280px, (min-width: 640px) 768px, calc(100vw/3)" loading="lazy" alt="1.png__PID:735430a5-fed7-4e9f-9d32-75c076abd07d" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-bXTejn eKvewz pf-733_"/></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-XxNYO eWQzGj pf-734_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0654/0725/4745/files/4_187fdc2a-3b73-42fa-9c32-3f5c0646037f_386x.png?v=1707202911" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0654/0725/4745/files/4_187fdc2a-3b73-42fa-9c32-3f5c0646037f.png?v=1707202911 1536w" width="926" height="1544" sizes="(min-width: 1536px) 1536px, (min-width: 1024px) 1280px, (min-width: 640px) 768px, calc(100vw/3)" loading="lazy" alt="4.png__PID:14735430-a5fe-47be-9f5d-3275c076abd0" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-bXTejn eKvewz pf-735_"/></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-6ca8" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-hAcGzb jHOovW pf-776_"><div style="--cw:801px" class="sc-eGPXGI cIlovf"><div class="sc-iCfMLu eehqFj pf-775_ pf-r